OL,3,CAfghans 'anxious' for result of
OL,4,Cinquiry into alleged special forces
OL,5,Cmurders
OL,7,FDr Nooralhaq Nasimi said families in
OL,8,FAfghanistan welcome the inquiry into
OL,9,Fthe alleged special forces murders of
OL,10,Fcivilians in 2011
OL,12,FAfghan families are "anxious" for the
OL,13,Foutcome of an inquiry into an alleged
OL,14,Fcover-up of special forces killings in
OL,15,FAfghanistan.
OL,17,FFormer defence secretary Sir Ben
OL,18,FWallace gave evidence in the inquiry
OL,19,Fon Monday, and has denied he "lacked
OL,20,Fcuriosity" when responding to the
OL,21,Fallegations.
