OL,7,FFormer veterans' minister Johnny
OL,8,FMercer wrote to Wallace in August 2020
OL,9,Fshortly after emails surfaced in The
OL,10,FSunday Times.
OL,12,FThey showed senior special forces
OL,13,Fofficers expressing serious concerns
OL,14,Fabout the killings of 33 people in 11
OL,15,Fnight raids in the war-torn nation in
OL,16,F2011.
