OL,7,FMercer previously told the Afghanistan
OL,8,FInquiry he was "angry" with Wallace,
OL,9,Fas well as the director of special
OL,10,Fforces and the chief of the general
OL,11,Fstaff.
OL,13,FHe claimed they had "not done the job
OL,14,Fthat was incumbent upon them with
OL,15,Ftheir rank and privileges in those
OL,16,Forganisations".
