OL,4,Cinquiry into alleged special forces
OL,5,Cmurders
OL,7,FHitting back at Mercer's claims on
OL,8,FMonday, the former defence secretary
OL,9,Fdescribed the claims that he lacked
OL,10,Fcuriosity as "highly inaccurate",
OL,11,Fadding: "I was absolutely inquisitive."
OL,13,FThe inquiry is examining whether a
OL,14,Fspecial forces unit, known to the
OL,15,Fprobe as UKSF1, had a policy of
OL,16,Fexecuting males of "fighting age" who
OL,17,Fposed no threat in Afghanistan between
OL,18,F2010 and 2013.
