OL,4,Cinquiry into alleged special forces
OL,5,Cmurders
OL,7,FAfghan families have accused UK
OL,8,Fspecial forces of conducting a
OL,9,F"campaign of murder" against
OL,10,Fcivilians, while senior officers and
OL,11,Fpersonnel at the Ministry of Defence
OL,12,F"sought to prevent adequate
OL,13,Finvestigation".
OL,15,FDr Nooralhaq Nasimi, head of the UK's
OL,16,FAfghanistan and Central Asian
OL,17,FAssociation called the inquiry a
OL,18,F"great step".
