OL,5,Cmurders
OL,7,F"We want to see that the inquiry will
OL,8,Fhave some kind of outcome to see why
OL,9,Fthis was happening, and how we can
OL,10,Fprevent it in the future and how we
OL,11,Fcan also contact the families who lost
OL,12,Ftheir families in Afghanistan," he
OL,13,Ftold ITV News.
OL,15,F"They are very anxious and they want
OL,16,Fto see the result of the inquiry."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
