OL,7,F"They want to see whether the British
OL,8,Farmed forces acted unlawfully. If they
OL,9,Facted unlawfully, there should be some
OL,10,Flegal measure against those
OL,11,Findividuals which caused serious
OL,12,Fcasualties against the civilians in
OL,13,FAfghanistan."
OL,15,F"The community are very anxious," he
OL,16,Fadded.
