OL,7,F"They welcome this inquiry. They are
OL,8,Fvery happy to see the result of this
OL,9,Finquiry to make sure those civilians
OL,10,Fwill have some sort of compensation
OL,11,Ffrom the British government."
OL,13,FWhen questioned at the inquiry,
OL,14,FWallace said: "Not only did I seek to
OL,15,Fdig deeper, I also even sought to dig
OL,16,Finternationally whether or not the
OL,17,Fassurances I'd been given were
OL,18,Ftruthful.
