OL,7,FThe former defence secretary replied:
OL,8,F"I did pay attention to it ` we are
OL,9,Fsitting in a public inquiry to get to
OL,10,Fthe bottom of it."
OL,12,FQuestioned on whether he was worried
OL,13,Fthat the allegations had been judged
OL,14,Fto be "broadly accurate", Wallace
OL,15,Fsaid: "I've said, I've never strayed
OL,16,Ffrom my belief that there may be more
OL,17,Fevidence out there."
