OL,7,FTwo Royal Military Police
OL,8,Finvestigations, codenamed Operation
OL,9,FNorthmoor and Operation Cestro, are
OL,10,Falso being scrutinised by the inquiry.
OL,12,FNo charges were brought under
OL,13,FOperation Northmoor ` a #10 million
OL,14,Finvestigation which was set up in 2014
OL,15,Fto examine allegations of executions
OL,16,Fby special forces, including those of
OL,17,Fchildren.
